---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Mangrove" description="Mangrove is a proudly Kiwi-owned operational consulting business helping organisations build businesses that are simpler, stronger and easier to run.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">About Mangrove</p>
      <h1>We're building the consultancy<br />we'd want to hire.</h1>
      <p>A proudly Kiwi-owned operational consulting business helping organisations build businesses that are simpler, stronger and easier to run. We improve systems, remove friction, and help teams do their best work.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Why we exist</h2>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 60ch; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        After more than a decade working across government and private organisations, Tash (Managing Director) kept seeing the same pattern: talented people spending more time working around broken systems than doing the work they were hired to do. Businesses adapting to their software instead of technology supporting how the business actually operates.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 60ch; line-height: 1.8;">
        Mangrove exists to change that. Businesses should become easier to run as they grow — not more complicated. The people you bring in to help should spend more time solving problems than creating paperwork.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-top: 4rem;">The promises we make</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Honest advice</h3>
          <p>Even if it means less work for us. We'll always tell you the truth about where we can add value — and when we think you don't need us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Practical over process</h3>
          <p>Solutions that your team will actually use — not endless workshops or reports that sit in a drawer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>You eventually need us less</h3>
          <p>Success is when your business improves long after we've left. We build capability, not dependency.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Outcomes over meetings</h3>
          <p>Your investment goes into solving problems. We keep administration lean so our time is spent delivering.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>5% back to community</h3>
          <p>We commit 5% of our consulting capacity to supporting charities, schools and community organisations — free of charge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Long-term thinking</h3>
          <p>Every project is an opportunity to learn. We continually ask: how could we have made this even better?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p>We'd love to hear from you — whether it's about working together or just a question.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
